Transform your browser start page with the whimsical Doraemon Theme extension! Every new tab features images of the beloved robotic cat, Doraemon, bringing a sense of fun and nostalgia to your browsing experience. Enjoy a delightful browsing experience with each new tab showcasing a different, charming scene from Doraemon's adventures.
This extension allows you to chose your search engine.
